        <A>; <B>; <A>.

<overlapping ranges> is a number:
    valid values:
        0 kg ... 10 kg.
        5 kg ... 15 kg.

<incomplete meaning> is a number:
    valid values:
        0 kg ... 100 kg.
    meaning of <incomplete meaning>:
        valid meanings:
            <low>; <high>.
        0 kg ... 50 kg:
            meaning of value = <low>.
            <status> = <low>.
        80 kg ... 100 kg:
            meaning of value = <high>.
            <status> = <high>.

<undefined usage> is a plan:
    before plan:
        <UndefinedVar> = 10 kg.
        information to <UnknownPerson> "Hello".

<unit mismatch assign> is a plan:
    before plan:
        <weight> = 10 <pounds>.
        <conflicting val> = 5 kg.
        <conflicting val> = 10 m.

